    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "912324_10_1515-1557",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1515-1557",
      "markText": "在阿赫兰跟在其他地方一样，由于缺乏时间，也缺少思考，人们不得不相爱而又不知道在相爱。",
      "totalCount": 5168,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=912324&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1515&rangeEnd=1557",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/886326405debc4886a87a2f?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1515&rangeEnd=1557"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "912324_14_14565-14609",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "14565-14609",
      "markText": "“世上没有任何东西值得人们为它而舍弃自己之所爱。但我不知道为什么，我也抛弃了我之所爱。”",
      "totalCount": 5100,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=912324&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=14565&rangeEnd=14609",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/886326405debc4886a87a2f?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=14565&rangeEnd=14609"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "912324_10_25041-25087",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "25041-25087",
      "markText": "既然人在死亡时只有被别人看见才受重视，分散在历史长河中的一亿尸体无非是想像中的一缕青烟而已。",
      "totalCount": 4378,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=912324&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=25041&rangeEnd=25087",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/886326405debc4886a87a2f?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=25041&rangeEnd=25087"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "912324_10_17680-17707",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "17680-17707",
      "markText": "“我惟一感兴趣的事，”我对他说，“是求得内心的安宁。”",
      "totalCount": 4301,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=912324&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=17680&rangeEnd=17707",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/886326405debc4886a87a2f?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=17680&rangeEnd=17707"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "912324_13_8898-8913",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "8898-8913",
      "markText": "习惯于绝望比绝望本身还要糟糕。",
      "totalCount": 4004,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=912324&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=8898&rangeEnd=8913",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/886326405debc4886a87a2f?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=8898&rangeEnd=8913"
